<view class='top'>
  <view class='t-tit'>钻石4C</view>
  <view class='t-section'>4C是您判断一颗钻石价值与品质的衡量标准。4C即钻石的克拉</view>
  <view class='t-section'>EZ Diamond秉承对完美的追求，致力于为客户甄选至臻至美的钻石，我们每一颗钻石的品质均是切工3EX、无荧光、无奶咖绿的优级钻石，且提供国际GIA证书。</view>
</view>

<view class='section'>
  <view class='s-tit'>
    <view class='st-left'>
      <image src='/images/class/img-carat.png' mode='widthFix' style='width: 110rpx'></image> 克拉 </view>
    <!-- <view class='st-right' data-data='carat' catchtap='playVideo'>查看视频</view> -->
  </view>
  <view class='video' >
    <video id="caratVideo" src="https://image.ezgold.cn/4Cvideo/video0.mp4"
       ></video>
  </view>
  <view class='s-info'>钻石重量以克拉（又称卡）计算。1克拉=200毫=0.2克。一克拉分为一百份，每一份称为一分。0.75克拉(3/4克拉)又称为75分，0.01克拉为1分。</view>
  <view class='s-show'>
    <view>滑动滑块，预览大小</view>
    <view style='margin-right: 80rpx; margin-bottom: 40rpx'>
      <image src='{{$simg}}/class/color/D@2x.png' class='sizeimg' mode='widthFix' style='transform: scale({{caratSize}}, {{caratSize}});'></image>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class='s-slide'>
    <view class='ss-hr'>
      <image src='/images/class/img-diamondhr.png' mode='widthFix' style="width: 710rpx;"></image>
      <view class='ss-tag'>
        <view></view>
        <view></view>
        <view></view>
        <view></view>
        <view></view>
        <view></view>
        <view></view>
        <view></view>
        <view></view>
      </view>
      <view class='ss-num'>
        <view wx:for="{{caratSizeList}}">{{item}}</view>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class='ss-scale' style='left: {{caratScale}}px' data-data='caratScale' data-offsetindex='{{caratScaleOffsetIndex}}' catchtouchstart='touchstart' catchtouchmove='touchmove' catchtouchend='touchend'>
      <image src='/images/class/img-size.png' mode='widthFix' style="width: 48rpx"></image>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class='s-unit'>:ct</view>
</view>


